title: Ford F-150  All Silver 20 inch OEM Wheel  2015-2017
h1title: 2015-2017 Ford F-150  All Silver 20" OEM Replacement Wheel
bodydescription:
This Ford genuine original equipment (OE) factory wheel has been Remanufactured by Wheels America the #1 wheel repair company.

it is refinished to the same high standard that we use on the hundreds of wheels we repair every day for Insurance Companies, Body Shops, Car Dealerships, and people like you.
condition_description: High-quality factory original remanufactured wheel that has gone through a 17-point safety inspection. Fully sandblasted (when appropriate), repaired, and powder coated to give the wheel a factory new appearance that has been approved by all major insurance companies as a replacement for a new wheel
